snippet.title: Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs BAN: India से हारकर Bangladesh ने कराई अपने Fans की बेइज़्ज़ती, हुए roast
snippet.description:
Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs BAN: India से हारकर Bangladesh ने कराई अपने Fans की बेइज़्ज़ती, हुए roast

#championstrophy2025 #indiavsbangladesh #indvsban  

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. कुल 8 टीमों को दो ग्रुप में बांटा गया है. पहले ग्रुप में भारत, पाकिस्तान, न्यूजीलैंड और बांग्लादेश शामिल हैं. वहीं, दूसरे ग्रुप में साउथ अफ्रीका, अफगानिस्तान, ऑस्ट्रेलिया और इंग्लैंड की टीमें हैं. टूर्नामेंट का फाइनल मैच 9 मार्च को होगा. भारतीय टीम अपना पहला मुकाबला बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ 6 विकेट से जीत चुकी है. भारत और पाकिस्तान के बीच महामुकाबला 23 फरवरी को दुबई में खेला जाएगा. इसके बाद भारतीय टीम ग्रुप स्टेज का तीसरा और आखिरी मुकाबला 2 मार्च को न्यूजीलैंड के खिलाफ खेलेगी. दोनों ग्रुप की टॉप-2 टीमें सेमीफाइनल के लिए क्वालीफाई करेंगी. लेकिन पाकिस्तान की चुनौती से पहले, बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम पर जीत अर्जित करते ही भारतीय क्रिकेट टीम ने एक अच्छी शुरुआत की है. इस जीत के बाद इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में भी ख़ुशी की लहर दौड़ गयी. बांग्लादेश की हार के बाद क्या कहा भारतीय फैंस ने? आगामी भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं भारतीय फैंस? क्यों जारी कर रहे हैं भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के लिए चेतावनी? बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस अब क्यों चाहते हैं पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को हराना? क्यों फूटा बांग्लादेशी फैंस का अपने कप्तान नजमुल होसैन शान्तो पर गुस्सा? भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस ने कैसे किया बांग्लादेशी फैंस का रोस्ट? जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच के चयन रस्तोगी की ये खास वीडियो सीधे दुबई इंटरनैशनल क्रिकेट स्टेडियम से, जहां वो बात कर रहे हैं बांग्लादेशी क्रिकेट फैंस और भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस से. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. After this victory, a wave of happiness also ran among the Indian cricket fans. What did the Indian fans say after Bangladesh's defeat? How eager are Indian fans for the upcoming India vs Pakistan match? Why are Indian cricket fans issuing warnings to Pakistan cricket team? Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.


India’s squad for ICC Champions Trophy, 2025: Rohit Sharma (Captain), Shubman Gill (Vice-captain), Virat Kohli, Shreyas Iyer, KL Rahul (WK), Rishabh Pant (WK), Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Mohd. Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Real Madrid 3-1 Man City | Mbappe (3) & Nico Goals
snippet.description:
Manchester City were knocked out this season’s UEFA Champions League after a 6-3 aggregate defeat to Real Madrid.
Pep Guardiola’s side were beaten 3-1 in the second leg at the Santiago Bernabeu with Kylian Mbappe scoring a hat-trick for the current European champions.

After a 3-2 defeat in the first leg at the Etihad, City fell further behind in the tie when the Frenchman scored the opener after just four minutes.

And we suffered a further early early setback with John Stones going off injured after just eight minutes while Erling Haaland was unable to feature in the fixture.

Mbappe scored two more either side of half-time before Nico scored his first goal for City in the dying minutes.

snippet.description:
PANDLOYAMMA PALLU PART-2 FULL SONG | TELUGU FOLK SONG  | SUMAN BADANAKAL| RAMYASRI | PARSHURAM NAGAM

https://youtu.be/YBvXt1rlKdo

#PandloyammaPallu #PandloyammaPalluSong #PandloyammaPalluTeluguSong #PandloyammaPalluFolkSong #parshuramnagam #latestnewfolksongs #newfolksongs #telugufolksongs  

పండ్లోయమ్మ పండ్లు PART-1 
👇FULL SONG OUT NOW👇
https://youtu.be/NYgYbNgWasE

పాట నేపథ్యం:
అక్రమాసంబంధ0 పెట్టుకున్న.. ఓ ఇల్లాలును తన కొడుకు నిలదీయడంతో.. ప్రబుద్ధుడు చంపేస్తాడు. శవాన్ని పూడ్చే క్రమంలో ఎన్నెన్నో ఇబ్బందులు ఎదురౌతాయి. 
దాంతో.. ఇంట్లో.. కొడుకుని నిలువునా కోసి.. ఉప్పుకారం దట్టించి.. కూర వండుతుంది. అనుకోకుండా అప్పుడే.. భర్త రావడంతో... అదే కూరను.. భర్తకు వడ్డిస్తుంది. 
భర్త తింటావుంటే.. కంచంలో కొడుకు యొక్క వెండి ఉంగరం..  బంగారి గొలుసు కనబడుతుంది.
అంతే... మళ్ళీ ఆ ప్రబుద్ధుడు వచ్చి భర్తని కొట్టి సంపుతాడు. 
కానీ అదంతా గమనిస్తున్న దొంగలు.. ఇంటికి గడియవేసి.. నిప్పు పెడతారు.  దాంతో ఈ రంకు జంట కూడా బూడిద అయిపోతుంది. 

ఆ దొంగలు.. పక్కనే చెట్టుకింద.. బండకు ఉన్న కాళికా అమ్మవారిని మొక్కుతారు. 
కాళీమాత ప్రత్యక్షమై.. "జీగర్ల పుల్ల" (సంజీవని) ఇస్తుంది. దాంతో.. చనిపోయిన వాళ్ళందరిని.. ఈ దొంగలు ఎలా బతికించారో.. అద్భుతమైన విజువల్స్ తో చూసి.. SHARE  చేయండి. 

నీతి:  తాత్కాలిక ఆనందాల కోసం.. పాకులాడితే.. నా అనుకునే వాళ్లనే కాదు.. చివరికి తనకు తాను సర్వం కోల్పోతారు అని.. చాటి చెప్పే పాట ఇది.

మీ.. పరశురాం నాగం
(రైటర్ & డైరెక్టర్)


LYRICS & DIRECTOR : PARSHURAM NAGAM

TUNE: MANDA RAMU,

SINGERS: SUMAN BADANAKAL & MANDA SARASWATHI RAMU

MUSIC:  INDRAJITT

CASTING:

కానీ అదంతా గమనిస్తున్న దొంగలు.. ఇంటికి గడియవేసి.. నిప్పు పెడతారు.  దాంతో ఈ రంకు జంట కూడా బూడిద అయిపోతుంది. 

ఆ దొంగలు.. పక్కనే చెట్టుకింద.. బండకు ఉన్న కాళికా అమ్మవారిని మొక్కుతారు. 
కాళీమాత ప్రత్యక్షమై.. "జీగర్ల పుల్ల" (సంజీవని) ఇస్తుంది. దాంతో.. చనిపోయిన వాళ్ళందరిని.. ఈ దొంగలు ఎలా బతికించారో.. అద్భుతమైన విజువల్స్ తో చూసి.. SHARE  చేయండి. 

నీతి:  తాత్కాలిక ఆనందాల కోసం.. పాకులాడితే.. నా అనుకునే వాళ్లనే కాదు.. చివరికి తనకు తాను సర్వం కోల్పోతారు అని.. చాటి చెప్పే పాట ఇది.

మీ.. పరశురాం నాగం
(రైటర్ & డైరెక్టర్)

snippet.title: Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs BAN: "Team India Pakistan को भी हराएगी", Indian Cricket Fans की ललकार
snippet.description:
Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs BAN: "Team India Pakistan को भी हराएगी", Indian Cricket Fans की ललकार

#championstrophy2025 #indiavsbangladesh #indvsban  

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. कुल 8 टीमों को दो ग्रुप में बांटा गया है. पहले ग्रुप में भारत, पाकिस्तान, न्यूजीलैंड और बांग्लादेश शामिल हैं. वहीं, दूसरे ग्रुप में साउथ अफ्रीका, अफगानिस्तान, ऑस्ट्रेलिया और इंग्लैंड की टीमें हैं. टूर्नामेंट का फाइनल मैच 9 मार्च को होगा. भारतीय टीम अपना पहला मुकाबला बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ 6 विकेट से जीत चुकी है. भारत और पाकिस्तान के बीच महामुकाबला 23 फरवरी को दुबई में खेला जाएगा. इसके बाद भारतीय टीम ग्रुप स्टेज का तीसरा और आखिरी मुकाबला 2 मार्च को न्यूजीलैंड के खिलाफ खेलेगी. दोनों ग्रुप की टॉप-2 टीमें सेमीफाइनल के लिए क्वालीफाई करेंगी. लेकिन पाकिस्तान की चुनौती से पहले, बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम पर जीत अर्जित करते ही भारतीय क्रिकेट टीम ने एक अच्छी शुरुआत की है. इस जीत के बाद इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में भी ख़ुशी की लहर दौड़ गयी. बांग्लादेश की हार के बाद क्या कहा भारतीय फैंस ने? आगामी भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं भारतीय फैंस? क्यों जारी कर रहे हैं भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के लिए चेतावनी? बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस अब क्यों चाहते हैं पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को हराना? क्यों फूटा बांग्लादेशी फैंस का अपने कप्तान नजमुल होसैन शान्तो पर गुस्सा? भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस ने कैसे किया बांग्लादेशी फैंस और पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस का रोस्ट? जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच के चयन रस्तोगी की ये खास वीडियो सीधे दुबई इंटरनैशनल क्रिकेट स्टेडियम से, जहां वो बात कर रहे हैं बांग्लादेशी क्रिकेट फैंस और भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस से. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? How did Indian cricket fans roast Bangladeshi fans and Pakistan cricket fans? To know more, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.

India’s squad for ICC Champions Trophy, 2025: Rohit Sharma (Captain), Shubman Gill (Vice-captain), Virat Kohli, Shreyas Iyer, KL Rahul (WK), Rishabh Pant (WK), Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Mohd. Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. कुल 8 टीमों को दो ग्रुप में बांटा गया है. पहले ग्रुप में भारत, पाकिस्तान, न्यूजीलैंड और बांग्लादेश शामिल हैं. वहीं, दूसरे ग्रुप में साउथ अफ्रीका, अफगानिस्तान, ऑस्ट्रेलिया और इंग्लैंड की टीमें हैं. टूर्नामेंट का फाइनल मैच 9 मार्च को होगा. भारतीय टीम अपना पहला मुकाबला बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ 6 विकेट से जीत चुकी है. भारत और पाकिस्तान के बीच महामुकाबला 23 फरवरी को दुबई में खेला जाएगा. इसके बाद भारतीय टीम ग्रुप स्टेज का तीसरा और आखिरी मुकाबला 2 मार्च को न्यूजीलैंड के खिलाफ खेलेगी. दोनों ग्रुप की टॉप-2 टीमें सेमीफाइनल के लिए क्वालीफाई करेंगी. लेकिन पाकिस्तान की चुनौती से पहले, बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम पर जीत अर्जित करते ही भारतीय क्रिकेट टीम ने एक अच्छी शुरुआत की है. इस जीत के बाद इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में भी ख़ुशी की लहर दौड़ गयी. बांग्लादेश की हार के बाद क्या कहा भारतीय फैंस ने? आगामी भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं भारतीय फैंस? क्यों जारी कर रहे हैं भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के लिए चेतावनी? बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस अब क्यों चाहते हैं पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को हराना? क्यों फूटा बांग्लादेशी फैंस का अपने कप्तान नजमुल होसैन शान्तो पर गुस्सा? भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस ने कैसे किया बांग्लादेशी फैंस और पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस का रोस्ट? जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच के चयन रस्तोगी की ये खास वीडियो सीधे दुबई इंटरनैशनल क्रिकेट स्टेडियम से, जहां वो बात कर रहे हैं बांग्लादेशी क्रिकेट फैंस और भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस से. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? How did Indian cricket fans roast Bangladeshi fans and Pakistan cricket fans? To know more, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.

India’s squad for ICC Champions Trophy, 2025: Rohit Sharma (Captain), Shubman Gill (Vice-captain), Virat Kohli, Shreyas Iyer, KL Rahul (WK), Rishabh Pant (WK), Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Mohd. Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 16e - February 19
snippet.description:
The latest iPhone at the greatest price — iPhone 16e is here. It’s built for Apple Intelligence and powered by A18, the latest-generation chip. It also comes with supersized battery life, a 48MP Fusion camera, and a durable design. 

Pricing, claims, and feature availability apply to the U.S. and may vary by region. For product details specific to your area, please refer to Apple.com.

snippet.title: KABULI PULAO | Afghani Biryani Style Rice | Afghanistan Special Recipe Cooking In Indian Village
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring the delicious and traditional Kabuli Pulao, a special rice dish from Afghanistan, cooked in our Indian village style. This flavorful pulao is made with fragrant basmati rice, tender meat, sweet carrots, and raisins, giving it a perfect balance of sweetness and spices.

Watch as we prepare this Afghani biryani-style rice using natural village cooking methods over a firewood stove. This is a must-try recipe for all pulao and biryani lovers!

We follow our traditional village cooking style using fresh ingredients and firewood. The result is an authentic, mouthwatering dish that you can easily try at home!

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Ek Badnaam Aashram Season 3 PT 2 - Official Trailer | Bobby Deol, Aaditi Pohankar | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Ek Badnaam Aashram Season 3 Part 2 - Official Trailer  

The wait is finally over! The most awaited series, Ek Badnaam Aashram, is back. With the visionary Prakash Jha at the helm and an incredible cast, Bobby Deol, Aaditi Pohankar, Chandan Roy Sanyal, Tridha Choudhury, and Darshan Kumar, this chapter promises to be bigger and more intense than ever.

#EkBadnaamAashram Season 3 Part 2 presented by #VimaalElaichi and co-powered by @LahoriZeera and #luxnitro, releasing on 27th Feb on Amazon MX Player

Cast -  Bobby Deol, Tridha Choudhury, Aaditi Pohankar, Chandan Roy Sanyal, Darshan Kumar, Sachin Shroff, Anurita Jha, Rajeev Siddharta 
Producer - Prakash Jha 
Production House -  Prakash Jha Productions 
Director - Prakash Jha 
Writers -  PJP Team, Madhvi Bhatt, Sanjay Masoom, Avinash Kumar
Genre - Crime, Thriller, Drama 

About Amazon MX Player - 
Amazon MX Player is India’s leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who’s your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter – Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more.

snippet.title: Dragon Public Review | Pradeep Ranganathan | Dragon Movie Review
snippet.description:
Dragon is an 2025 Indian Tamil-language film written and directed by Ashwath Marimuthu, from a story he co-wrote with Pradeep Ranganathan, and produced by AGS Entertainment. The film stars Pradeep in the titular role, alongside Anupama Parameswaran, Kayadu Lohar, George Maryan, Indumathy Manikandan, K. S. Ravikumar, Gautham Vasudev Menon, Mysskin, VJ Siddhu and Harshath Khan. The film has music composed by Leon James, cinematography handled by Niketh Bommi and editing by Pradeep E. Ragav. Dragon movie releasing worldwide today. In this video we are presenting you the Public Review of Dragon from audience in theatres. Dragon FDFS Review is taken from Chennai.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4327 - Tapu aur Sonu ki Bat Sun kar Bhide ke Ude Hosh?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

snippet.title: Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs BAN: Team India से हारकर फूटा Bangladeshi Cricket Fans का गुस्सा
snippet.description:
#championstrophy2025 #indiavsbangladesh #indvsban  

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. कुल 8 टीमों को दो ग्रुप में बांटा गया है. पहले ग्रुप में भारत, पाकिस्तान, न्यूजीलैंड और बांग्लादेश शामिल हैं. वहीं, दूसरे ग्रुप में साउथ अफ्रीका, अफगानिस्तान, ऑस्ट्रेलिया और इंग्लैंड की टीमें हैं. टूर्नामेंट का फाइनल मैच 9 मार्च को होगा. भारतीय टीम अपना पहला मुकाबला बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ 6 विकेट से जीत चुकी है. भारत और पाकिस्तान के बीच महामुकाबला 23 फरवरी को दुबई में खेला जाएगा. इसके बाद भारतीय टीम ग्रुप स्टेज का तीसरा और आखिरी मुकाबला 2 मार्च को न्यूजीलैंड के खिलाफ खेलेगी. दोनों ग्रुप की टॉप-2 टीमें सेमीफाइनल के लिए क्वालीफाई करेंगी. लेकिन पाकिस्तान की चुनौती से पहले, बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम पर जीत अर्जित करते ही भारतीय क्रिकेट टीम ने एक अच्छी शुरुआत की है. इस जीत के बाद इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में भी ख़ुशी की लहर दौड़ गयी. बांग्लादेश की हार के बाद क्या कहा भारतीय फैंस ने? आगामी भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं भारतीय फैंस? क्यों जारी कर रहे हैं भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के लिए चेतावनी? बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस अब क्यों चाहते हैं पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को हराना? क्यों फूटा बांग्लादेशी फैंस का अपने कप्तान नजमुल होसैन शान्तो पर गुस्सा? जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच के चयन रस्तोगी की ये खास वीडियो सीधे दुबई इंटरनैशनल क्रिकेट स्टेडियम से, जहां वो बात कर रहे हैं बांग्लादेशी क्रिकेट फैंस और भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस से. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. After this victory, a wave of happiness also ran among the Indian cricket fans. What did the Indian fans say after Bangladesh's defeat? How eager are Indian fans for the upcoming India vs Pakistan match? Why are Indian cricket fans issuing warnings to Pakistan cricket team? Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.


India’s squad for ICC Champions Trophy, 2025: Rohit Sharma (Captain), Shubman Gill (Vice-captain), Virat Kohli, Shreyas Iyer, KL Rahul (WK), Rishabh Pant (WK), Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Mohd. Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. कुल 8 टीमों को दो ग्रुप में बांटा गया है. पहले ग्रुप में भारत, पाकिस्तान, न्यूजीलैंड और बांग्लादेश शामिल हैं. वहीं, दूसरे ग्रुप में साउथ अफ्रीका, अफगानिस्तान, ऑस्ट्रेलिया और इंग्लैंड की टीमें हैं. टूर्नामेंट का फाइनल मैच 9 मार्च को होगा. भारतीय टीम अपना पहला मुकाबला बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ 6 विकेट से जीत चुकी है. भारत और पाकिस्तान के बीच महामुकाबला 23 फरवरी को दुबई में खेला जाएगा. इसके बाद भारतीय टीम ग्रुप स्टेज का तीसरा और आखिरी मुकाबला 2 मार्च को न्यूजीलैंड के खिलाफ खेलेगी. दोनों ग्रुप की टॉप-2 टीमें सेमीफाइनल के लिए क्वालीफाई करेंगी. लेकिन पाकिस्तान की चुनौती से पहले, बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम पर जीत अर्जित करते ही भारतीय क्रिकेट टीम ने एक अच्छी शुरुआत की है. इस जीत के बाद इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में भी ख़ुशी की लहर दौड़ गयी. बांग्लादेश की हार के बाद क्या कहा भारतीय फैंस ने? आगामी भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं भारतीय फैंस? क्यों जारी कर रहे हैं भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के लिए चेतावनी? बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस अब क्यों चाहते हैं पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को हराना? क्यों फूटा बांग्लादेशी फैंस का अपने कप्तान नजमुल होसैन शान्तो पर गुस्सा? जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच के चयन रस्तोगी की ये खास वीडियो सीधे दुबई इंटरनैशनल क्रिकेट स्टेडियम से, जहां वो बात कर रहे हैं बांग्लादेशी क्रिकेट फैंस और भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस से. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. After this victory, a wave of happiness also ran among the Indian cricket fans. What did the Indian fans say after Bangladesh's defeat? How eager are Indian fans for the upcoming India vs Pakistan match? Why are Indian cricket fans issuing warnings to Pakistan cricket team? Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.


India’s squad for ICC Champions Trophy, 2025: Rohit Sharma (Captain), Shubman Gill (Vice-captain), Virat Kohli, Shreyas Iyer, KL Rahul (WK), Rishabh Pant (WK), Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Mohd. Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

snippet.title: The Real Ways It Spreads | NSACS | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
HIV  can be transmitted through specific routes, and understanding them is crucial for prevention. In this video, we break down the main ways HIV spreads, including:

✔️ Unprotected sexual contact
✔️ Sharing needles or syringes
✔️ From mother to child (during pregnancy, childbirth, or breastfeeding)
✔️ Blood transfusions (though rare due to screening)

Stay informed and take precautions to prevent HIV transmission. If you found this video helpful, don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe for more health awareness content!

With a visually stunning VFX video, we bring to life the awe-inspiring aura of Mahakaal.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: KIIT University Shocker | After Death On Campus - Nepalese Students Thrown Out | Akash Banerjee
snippet.description:
After a tragic death on campus - protesting Nepalese students (who were demanding answers from the Administration) were shocking thrown out from campus and dumped to the railway station without tickers.

The students from Nepal fought back - even forcing the Nepalese PM to intervene and activate diplomatic channels. After the news went viral - the college administration did a massive u-turn -.... asking students to rejoin immediately. But why did a young girl take her life - who's the politicians's son who's been arrested and what was the University trying to hide???

Suzhal – The Vortex Season 2 Official Trailer 
Starring Kathir, Aishwarya Rajesh, Lal, Saravanan, Manjima Mohan, ‘Kayal’ Chandran, Gouri G Kishan, Samyuktha Viola Viswanathan, Monisha Blessy, Rini, Shrisha, Abhirami Bose, Nikhila Sankar, Kalaivani Bhaskar, Ashwini Nambiar, Chandini Tamilarasan & others
Created by Pushkar & Gayatri
Directed by Bramma & Sarjun KM
Production House : Wallwatcher Films

Official Release Date Feb 28, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Created by Pushkar and Gayatri, Suzhal - The Vortex S2 begins with the shocking murder of senior activist lawyer Chellapa, who defended Nandini. Set against the backdrop of the massive Ashtakaali Festival, the case unravels family secrets and betrayals, and acts in the past that cast long shadows on the present.

Episode 4325: Society Rules For Bhoothnath 
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide meets Bhootnath to discuss the society's rules, while Taarak questions Jethalal about Tapu's marriage.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4325 | 19 Feb 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
